PrecisAmendments to the QUEEN'S REGULATIONS AND ORDERS FOR THE CANADIAN FORCES which revise Article 209.51 (Compassionate Travel Assistance) by extending compassionate travel benefits to all members of the Canadian Armed Forces who are not covered by the Military Foreign Service Regulations, and repeal Article 209.826.
